Adafruit Itsybitsy M4 hardware and INA226 IC used for this project.

# Project Structure

1. Servo control (60 to 120)
    Modes: 
    1. All: Default device is 000 (All device)
    2. Individual: User can Device number in chain from total device detection
    Command: 00x,servo,angle [x: device, angle: value]

2. Current control (0mA to 1500mA)
    Modes:
    1. All: Default device is 000 (All device)    
    2. Individual: User can Device number in chain from total device detection
    command: 00x,current,mA [x: device, mA: value]

- Do not change the project design structure.

